---
import {Markdown} from 'astro/components'
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Title from '$components/Title'
---

<BaseLayout title="Donate">
	<div class="flex flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap">
		<div class="w-full md:w-1/3 md:pr-3 mb-3">
			<div class="content-container">
				<Title title="Donate" subtitle="Here" classes="text-center"/>
				<a href="https://poweredbyshunpike.org/c/PBS/a/honkfestwest" class="block">
					<img class="rounded mx-auto p-2 h-26 bg-[#f4efdf] border-accent-color border-2" src="https://ik.imagekit.io/thegoldendino/hfw/sponsors/shunpike_IPvJZWnb8w.gif?updatedAt=1628178274416" alt="Shunpike The Business of Art"/>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="w-full md:w-2/3 md:pl-3">
			<div class="content-container">
				<div class="content">
					<Markdown>
						Your contributions help make this event possible. Through the generous efforts of our shared community, we’ll keep bringing music to the streets and parks of Seattle’s neighborhoods.
						<br/>
						HONK! Fest West is fiscally sponsored by [Shunpike](https://poweredbyshunpike.org/c/PBS/a/honkfestwest) which is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization. Donations made through Shunpike are tax deductible to the fullest extent of the law.
						<br/>
						Please get in touch with us at [info@honkfestwest.org](mailto:info@honkfestwest.org) if you’d like another option, or would like to arrange donations of goods or services. Thanks so much, and we hope to see you at HONK! Fest West.
					</Markdown>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>